{
  "title": "Wizards of Morcar",
  "image": "../images/purchases/heroquest/Heroquest-Wizards-Of-Morcar.jpg",
  "imageAlt": "HeroQuest: Wizards of Morcar Box",
  "description": [
    {
      "paragraph": "Loretome has foreseen the alliance of the realm's most powerful wizards, all of whom have agreed to do Zargon's dark bidding. This time, Zargon seeks the legendary magic of 1000 Dread sorcerers locked away in the High Alter of the Northern Dread Wastes. Stop Zargon from getting his hands on the power-or he will be unstoppable!"
    },
    {
      "paragraph": "The expansion includes 10 new quests and additional miniatures. Players can take on the role of a Female Wizard."
    },
    {
      "paragraph": "This expansion is designed to be used in conjunction with the original HeroQuest game, and players will need the core box to fully enjoy the new content and features introduced in \"Wizards of Morcar.\""
    }
  ],
